Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.28,2:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}梵蒂冈会计师失踪\N“上帝的银行家”消失，未给罗马家中留话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲爱的孩子们…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My dear children...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我迁居纽约已有多年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it is now better than several years since I moved to New York
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我并未如愿常常见到你们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I haven't seen you as much as I would like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们会来参加这次教宗嘉奖的仪式\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hope you will come to this ceremony of papal honors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表彰我的慈善事业\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}given for my charitable work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上唯一的财富是孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The only wealth in this world is children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过世间所有的金钱、权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}More than all the money, power on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是我的珍宝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you are my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼和玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony and Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然为了你们的最佳利益，我将你们的教育托付给你们母亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}although I entrusted your education to your mother for your own best interests
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我多么期待见到你们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you know how I look forward to seeing you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待咱们生命中一个和谐的新阶段\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and to a new period of harmony in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你们能说动母亲来参加本次典礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Perhaps you might prevail upon your mother to come to this celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且时不时地…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and that from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全家人能互相见见面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we can all see each other at family functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何，我依然是，爱你们的父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anyway, I remain, your loving father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万福玛利亚  充满恩惠\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hail Mary, full of grace
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐福予汝等之妇女\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}blessed art Thou amongst women
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐福乃孕育于汝子宫之胎，基督\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and blessed is the fruit of Thy womb,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣玛利亚，上帝之母\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Holy Mary, mother of God
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我等罪人祈祷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}pray for us sinners
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全能上帝，降福这殉道士圣塞巴斯蒂安徽章\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Almighty God, bless the insignia of Saint Sebastian the Martyr
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿为其赐予者带来圣光\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that it may contribute to the sacredness of him to whom it is given.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你，迈克尔…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you, Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否承诺忠于本教令之崇高宗旨…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}promise to be faithful to the noble purposes of this order
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对贫者、穷者及病者予以特别关怀？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to have a special care for the poor, the needy and those who are ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当如此承诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I do so promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿全能之圣父圣子圣灵 降福于你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}May the blessing of Almighty God Father, Son, and Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你同在 以迨永远\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}descend upon you and remain with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特，我们的名字不在名单上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, our name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写上去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Write it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼西尼  M-A-N-I-N-I\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mancini. M-A-N-C-l-N-I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is there a problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题，我的名字不在名单上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No problem, my name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你没在名单上，你得即刻离开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, you're not on the list, you have to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没别的办法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想跟我跳舞吗，宝贝？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You want to dance with me, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔，乔，这是文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joe, Joe, it's Vinnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼，没关系，他们是客人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie, it's okay. These are our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 抱歉，大卫  - 没关系，没关系\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I'm sorry, Dave. -It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼，欢迎参加宴会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie, welcome to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次见到你真好，这是我丈夫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's good to see you again. This is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我儿子安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is my son, Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣塞巴斯蒂安勋章在天主教廷…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The order of Saint Sebastian is one of the highest honors
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是颁给俗世人的最高荣誉之一\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Catholic Church can bestow upon a layman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本奖章，首次由教皇格里哥利颁发\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The award was first granted by Pope Gregory
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生与拉斯维加斯赌场的关系怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about Mr. Corleone's connections with Las Vegas gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料袋中有些照片…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Presskits have pictures of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他跟黑社会的牵连呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about his involvement with the underworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说废话了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cut the crap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇，圣父本人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope, the Holy Father himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派人在这一天赐福迈克尔·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has this very day blessed Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你比教皇更懂？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You think you know better than the pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去啊，去啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do it, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特   - 干嘛？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent! -Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她爱你  - 是吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-She loves you. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，文森，我记得你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi Vincent. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得我？在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You remember me? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我们一起参加的派对上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}From the last time when we were at a party together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前去过俱乐部？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you come down to the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，是个婚礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, it was a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时8岁，你15岁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was 8; and you were 15
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我15岁时有一堆女朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well I, I had a lot of girlfriends when I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8岁的吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}8 year olds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是8岁的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Especially 8 year olds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where's Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托哪位叫玛丽一声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Would somebody please tell Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅，阁下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗，你还没给我问候吻呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know? You haven't kissed me hello yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚相见总要亲吻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Relatives always kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，咱们还是亲戚？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, now we're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的小堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm your little cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你个提示  他是意大利人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll give you a hint: he's Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，我们一直在等你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, we've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住，声音要低，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember now, keep your voice low, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有微笑，别忘了笑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And smile! Don't forget to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·柯利昂尼基金会荣誉主席\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The honorary chairman of the Vito Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿 玛丽·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My daughter, Mary Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我继承了我父亲爱演说的习惯\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I inherited my father's love for speech making
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是这样的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But here it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·柯利昂尼基金会在世界各国济贫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vito Corleone Foundation helps the impoverished of every country
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补助艺术家，资助医学研究\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}gives grants to artists, funds medical research
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是致力于西西里的复兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and is particularly dedicated to the resurrection of Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔戴总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Archbishop Gilday
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是给西西里穷人的一亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here is, $100,000,000 for the poor of Sicily
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以维多·柯利昂尼之名捐出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in the name of Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要全花在一个地方上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't spend it all in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为西西里做了一件伟大的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you've done a wonderful thing for Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们惟愿钱用在有需要的人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, let's just hope the money gets to the people who need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的部分…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But the most important part
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰尼·方廷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Johnny Fontane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴加入大家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm happy to be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愿意让大家加入我 为迈克尔·柯利昂尼的表彰添彩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I'd like you to join me in honoring Commendatore Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特别为我们的主人和教父准备了礼物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I have something special for our host and Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恰好知道他最喜爱的歌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just happen to know his favorite song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你上哪儿去？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你最喜欢的歌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your favorite song!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去厨房 听托尼·班奈特{\fs12}爵士乐大师{\r}的唱片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, I'm off here to the kitchen to hear some Tony Bennett records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你最喜欢的歌“他所有的香肠”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your favorite song "Sausage His Own".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，我正要去吃香肠三明治，就回来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right; a sausage sandwich! I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hello Kay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜，迈克尔，这真是很大的荣耀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well congratulations, Michael, that's really quite an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是贵了一点，你说呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a little expensive, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很久了，对吧？  - 对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-It's been a long time, hasn't it? -Uh huh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 八年了  - 是啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Eight years. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的气色…好极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You look, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子有事要告诉你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your son has something he wants to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为他而来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当律师有什么不好？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's wrong with being a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有，只是他不想当\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nothing, except he doesn't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他热爱音乐  他想以音乐为生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loves music, he wants his life to be in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐很好，我爱音乐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well music is great. I love music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他应该有始有终\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But he should finish what he started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走自己的路\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己的路？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 专业歌手？  - 正是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Professional singer? -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要是…要是你失败了呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And what happens what happens if you fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会失败的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人总是相信如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Men always believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有个法律学位，你就有了保险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you have a Law degree, you're taking out insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后你可以想干嘛干嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After that you can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你可以为我做事…  - 我绝不会为你做事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You can work for me... -I will never work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有许多糟糕的回忆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个家庭都有糟糕的回忆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Every family has bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远会是你的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will always be your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我绝不会与你的事业沾边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I will never have anything to do with your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修完法律学位\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}finish the Law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从你那儿来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that he got from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句“不要”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本应该帮我说服他，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could have helped me to convince him, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说服他干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, convince him of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抛弃了自己的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He throws his life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抛弃了成就\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He throws greatness away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是成就？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is greatness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗，迈克尔，因为你备受尊敬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know Michael, now that you're so respectable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你比以往任何时候更加危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think you're more dangerous than you ever were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我更喜欢还是普通黑手党打手时的你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In fact, I preferred you when you were just a common Mafia hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们能不能谈谈常识？  - 好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-now can we talk common sense here? -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼知道你杀了弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tony knows that you killed Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里是为了什么，凯伊？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you come here for, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来保护我儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here to protect my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是来看你被你的教会装扮的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I didn't come here to see you disguised by your church.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那是一场可耻的典礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think that was a shameful ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耗费一生保护我的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent my life protecting my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耗费一生保护我的家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent my life protecting my FAMILY!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，咱们讲道理好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. Let's be reasonable, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的大事，对吧迈克尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's your big thing, isn't it, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以谋杀做后备\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Backed up by murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，天啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh God
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恨我  你恨我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You hate me, you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不恨你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't hate you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畏惧你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I dread you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽我所能，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I did what I could， Kay，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来保护 你们所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to protect, all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受世上的恐怖威胁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}from the horrors of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你成了我的恐惧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But you became my horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过孩子们依然爱你  尤其是玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The children still love you though. Especially Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以在这基础上建立\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We can build on that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们试试吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你让托尼自由去走自己的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only if you let Tony go free to have his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远离你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让托尼走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll let Tony go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那双鞋可以用来伤人了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could hurt somebody with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你工作挺累的，我带你四处看看吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You've been working too hard, let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我采访到迈克尔·柯利昂尼吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can you get me an interview with Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，我是他的亲戚，但我做不到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, no. I'm a relative but I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的可以为你效劳的吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What else can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得帅但没用\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Handsome but useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事，我赌一赌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's okay. I'll gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢赌？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You like to gamble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去亚特兰大城\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So we go to Atlantic City
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的地盘，我让你看看怎么赌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My town. I'll show you how to gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊，不过我喜欢赢，你怎么知道哪一把能赢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, but I like to win. How will I know what numbers to pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像个输家吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I look okay like a guy who's gonna lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那人样子可怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Spooky looking guy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的人来迈克尔·柯利昂尼家干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is a guy like that doing at Michael Corleone's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是乔伊·札萨的斗犬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's Joey Zasa's bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识那人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我认识那个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah I know that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人，他名叫安东尼·斯库里亚诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That guy, his name is Anthony Squigliaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们称他为“蚂蚁”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They call him The Ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把子弹浸氰化物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He dips his bullets in Cyanide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来表示敬意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came to pay my respects
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我父亲的友谊增辉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You honor my father's friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的教女在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where is my goddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康斯坦琪娅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Constanzia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前我还用这双衰老的手抱过你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was not so long ago I held you in these old hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Piachere? Cominar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，我站着可以了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no. I stand; I stand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我已失去全部毒牙，全部年轻的活力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, I lost all the venom, all the juice of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了对女人的欲望\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I lost the lust for women
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在我的头脑清楚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and now my mind is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对上帝的责任也清楚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My duty to God is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要特别请你帮忙\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a special favor to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的名字附加在柯利昂尼基金会上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}attach my name to the Vito Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你我能在名义和精神上联合\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so that you and I can be joined in name and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百万美金\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One million dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Godfather
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛，你真善心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello, you have such heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走，我们去品几杯意大利酒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come, let's go and sample some of Italy vino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈对这些股东一无所知\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vatican knows nothing about these shareholders
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向来忧心忡忡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a tendency to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已大幅增进了我们的地位，自然我会担忧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've increased our position substantially and naturally I worry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，洛缪，别担心了，我们有共识的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Romeo, stop worrying. We have an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好  你以为我的灰发哪儿来的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. How do you think I got this grey hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就两秒钟  - 法兰克，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-two seconds -Frank, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你对游泳池建设的贡献\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you very much for your contribution to the Board's swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外我们需要你帮助山姆·华莱士竞选法官\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And we need your help on Sam Wallace's candidacy for judgeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们总是用得着一个好法官的  - 谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We always can use a good judge -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下，我的教子安德鲁·黑根\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Excellency, my Godson, Andrew Hagan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兄弟汤姆·黑根的大儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}my brother Tom Hagan's eldest boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他协助格林宁主教已经…  - 三年  - …三年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's been assistant to Bishop Greening for... - 3 years - 3 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期望调任梵蒂冈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hoping for an assignment to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马总是有位置给优秀的年轻牧师的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's always a place in Rome for a fine young priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的母亲 泰瑞莎·黑根\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His mother Theresa Hagen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔戴总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Archbishop Gilday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Honored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生，你好，我是格蕾丝·汉密尔顿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone. Hi, Grace Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·曼西尼答应过会跟你提起我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent Mancini promised that he'd tell you about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说也许你会见我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that maybe you'd see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特·曼西尼提到过她？  - 没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent Mancini called about her? -No
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝，你答应过我要待在那边的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grace, you promised me you'd stay up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道  - 两次  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I know. -Twice. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨露面了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让他在门厅等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've got him waiting in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说要亲自恭贺并向你致敬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Says he wants to personally congratulate you and show his respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非得见他吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I have to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说你是他的老板{\fs12}[法语]{\r}，而且他只要一分钟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He says you're his patrone and he only wants a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey Vinnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜欢的姑姑是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's your favorite Aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我会跟迈克尔谈谈你的小麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Today I'm gonna talk to Michael about your little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿你早跟我说，康\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wish you would have warned me Conn',
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以穿好点的衣服来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could have worn a better suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇协会选了你…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Meucci Association has elected you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为年度意裔美国人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}their Italian-American Man of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Meucci
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's Meucci?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是意裔美国人，发明了电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's the Italian-American who invented the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比亚历山大·格拉汉姆·贝尔早了一年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He did it one year before Alexander Graham Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你在这一天来到我家的原因吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And this is the reason you've come to my home on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喂鱼{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go feed the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鞋子里有颗硌人的石头，柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I got a stone in my shoe, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个替我干活的小瘪三\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A two-bit punk who works for me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个，自以为是你亲戚的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The one who, thinks he's related to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.14,0:24:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个私生子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.50,0:24:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·曼西尼  他在宴会上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent Mancini. He's at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.23,0:24:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我们谈谈比较好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think it's good we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用，谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.35,0:24:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要搞清楚 它是我的麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I want to find out if it is my problem
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.80,0:24:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你的麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}or your problem
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.35,0:25:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔，你的生意是你的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joe, your business is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.43,0:25:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既无利益也不分红\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have no interests or percentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.10,0:25:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是外人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.77,0:25:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它就是我的麻烦了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then it's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你认识文森特·曼西尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, you know Vincent Mancini
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.85,0:25:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑尼的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sonny's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗，柯利昂尼先生？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How you doin' Mr. Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.93,0:25:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺好的，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm doin' good. How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.35,0:25:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 挺好  - 宴会不错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Good. -Good party.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你喜欢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.03,0:25:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，我只好溜进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, I had to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.47,0:25:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你专门打扮了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, you're dressed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.75,0:25:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.25,0:25:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和乔·札萨先生有什么过节？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what's the trouble between you and Mr. Joe Zasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.10,0:25:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有麻烦，我会摆平的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's trouble. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样挺愚蠢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's foolish of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蠢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Foolish of ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.35,0:25:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才有点蠢，你不觉得吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a little foolish of this guy don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.62,0:25:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.20,0:25:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脾气像他父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Temper like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔·札萨先生目前拥有…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Joe Zasa now owns
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.20,0:26:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家在纽约曾经的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what used to be the Corleone family business, in New York.
