Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.91,0:35:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.15,0:35:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做一件事说服你，别被吓着\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna do something to convince you. Don't get frightened.
