Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.52,0:35:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下刀，快，放下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Drop the knife，g'head, DROP IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.39,0:35:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子，坐下，我有话跟你说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good boy. Sit down I wanna talk to you.
