Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.81,0:35:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谁派你来的？  - 该死\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Who sent you? -Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.61,0:35:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，告诉我，谁派你来的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}C'mon tell me, who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.53,0:35:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.35,0:35:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看过这家伙没？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take a good look at this guy?
