Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.95,0:36:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才打算让他们杀了我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were gonna let them kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.85,0:36:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我不会让你有什么事的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I wasn't gonna let anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.25,0:36:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这头猪，你他妈变态\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You pig! You sick fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.95,0:36:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，亲，那就是赌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}C'mon sweetheart, that's gambling.
