Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.70,0:36:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.88,0:36:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有枪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You had a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.44,0:36:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只有刀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They only had a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.37,0:36:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本可以叫他们投降\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could have talked them into surrendering;
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.02,0:37:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们交给警察\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}handed them over to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札萨派来这俩人，我只是给他一个信息，就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Zasa sent these guys, I just sent him a message. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.22,0:37:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他又得回敬你一个信息\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now he has to send you a message back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.88,0:37:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨要回敬我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa's gonna send ME a message back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.95,0:37:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨想回敬我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa's gonna send ME a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.61,0:37:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做得对，他问出了札萨的名字\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He did the right thing, he got Zasa's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.80,0:37:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛非得把乔伊·札萨扯进来？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What has Joey Zasa got to with anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨是个狂人，乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa's a potzle. Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.04,0:37:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，你就是你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, you are what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.34,0:37:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的天性\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.74,0:37:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你紧跟着我，什么也别做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You stay close to me. You don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.28,0:37:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把嘴巴闭紧 眼睛睁大\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You keep your mouth shut, and your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.81,0:37:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你照我的吩咐做，懂不懂？  - 我懂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-And you do what I tell you. Understand? -Understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.62,0:37:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我跟委员会之间有问题，年轻人  - 这我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I got problems with the Commission, young man. -I know thar.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.86,0:37:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，你是越帮越忙\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes. You don't make them easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.02,0:37:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道，也不是我想要搞出这种事的，你看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand that, it wasn't my idea that this happened, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.73,0:37:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，走吧，出去吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. Go on, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.42,0:37:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.88,0:37:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.80,0:37:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们会怕你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now they'll fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他们应该怕你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe they should fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.54,0:37:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BJ，抱歉，什么事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}B.J., excuse me. what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.45,0:38:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，总主教刚回了电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, the Archbishop just called back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.41,0:38:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为你的投标做了一些出色的安排\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's arranged some amazing things for your bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.15,0:38:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传效果显著，你成了慈善界的新洛克菲勒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Publicity is phenomenal. You're the new Rockefeller of philanthropy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在这里签名\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sign right here please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.97,0:38:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时代的确变了，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Times do change, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.60,0:38:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲讨厌基金会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My father hated foundations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.90,0:38:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜欢亲力亲为\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loved doing it by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.32,0:38:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人对人 但我们，我们不一样了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Man to man. But we, we're different, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那些大企业没什么不同\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's no different than any large corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以小钱控制大钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We control a lot of money with very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交最少的税 不受政府控制\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Minimize taxes, with, no government control.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.75,0:38:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.12,0:38:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.78,0:38:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.55,0:38:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 教父  - 要去罗马了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Godfather.  -Off to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.89,0:38:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要感激你为我做的一切\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted to thank you for all you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.79,0:38:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 来，你要跟我们一起吃点早餐吗？  - 不，谢谢，不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-C'mon, you want to have some breakfast with us? -No thanks I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:38:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，你的意大利语怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. How's your Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要练习{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Devo fare un po'di pratica.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.44,0:39:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他父亲是个大律师  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-His father was a great lawyer. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.05,0:39:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没活到看他被授圣职，我看到了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Didn't live to see him ordained. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过那种场面吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ever seen one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.74,0:39:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮，我以你为傲，来，我送你出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, beautiful. I was so proud. Come on, let me walk you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.45,0:39:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁，要是你在梵蒂冈听到什么流言…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew, if you hear any rumors flying around the Vatican
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.56,0:39:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要让我知道  - 不不，安德鲁是真信仰\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-you let me know about it  -Oh no, no. Andrew has the true faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.36,0:39:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.40,0:39:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.54,0:39:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是点根蜡烛而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And not just to light a little candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.34,0:39:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天赋，是能够劝服人们…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My, gift, was to be able to persuade people,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.03,0:39:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向神圣的教会捐献\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to give, to the Holy Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.15,0:39:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是，罗马决定让我掌管梵蒂冈银行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then, Rome decides, to put me in charge of the Vatican bank.
