Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.65,0:40:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿祷告能够…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, if only prayer could,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.30,0:40:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补足我们7亿美元的赤字\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}pay off our seven-hundred million dollar deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.93,0:40:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7亿6千9百万\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Seven-hundred and sixty-nine million.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.33,0:40:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会拥有一家大公司的25%…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Church owns 25% of a large corporation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.61,0:40:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我说的这家公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the one I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一大地主\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Largest landlord on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房地产遍布全球，价值60亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}real estate all over the world worth six billion dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.19,0:41:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要控股，梵蒂冈的一票是必需的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And the Vatican vote is necessary for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不不，你弄错了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. No, no. You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.63,0:41:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一个人能决定的问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This isn't a question of one person deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.64,0:41:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一票决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}one deciding vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.27,0:41:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟世上任何其他公司一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is like any other company in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有董事，我们有规章\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have directors, we have rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.10,0:41:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有非常古老的规章\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have very old rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.07,0:41:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得教宗本人，批准你才行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope himself, would have to approve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已卖掉了各个赌场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've sold the casinos
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.85,0:41:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有与赌博相关的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all businesses having to do with gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有兴趣，也无投资…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have no interests, or investments
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.39,0:41:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在任何非法事业上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in anything illegitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.47,0:41:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家已准备好将5亿美元存入梵蒂冈银行…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Corleone's prepared to deposit 500 million dollars in the Vatican bank
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.17,0:41:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只等柯利昂尼先生拿到“屹莫比”的过半控制权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}at such time as Mr. Corleone receives majority control of Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.01,0:41:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”能够成为一个新事物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare could be something new
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.88,0:41:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家欧洲企业集团\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a European conglomerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.38,0:42:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜有家族 控制这样的公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Few families, have control of such a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.85,0:42:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今日的世界…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It seems in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.82,0:42:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免除债务的权力…强过了宽恕的权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the power to absolve debt is greater than the power of forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.33,0:42:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Six hundred million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.27,0:42:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要高估了宽恕的权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't overestimate the power of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.76,0:42:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟“屹莫比”的这笔交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}this deal with Immobiliare...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.95,0:42:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你成为世上最富有的人之一\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}can make you one of the richest men in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.22,0:42:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的整个过往史，以及你家族的历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your whole past history and the history of your family
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.87,0:42:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将被洗刷干净\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}will be washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.55,0:42:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}600 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.33,0:43:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动议讨论事项\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The motion under discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.14,0:43:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于柯利昂尼集团所提议\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}relates to Corleone Group's proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.40,0:43:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要取得一亿新发A级表决权股票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to acquire 100 million newly issued class "A' ' voting shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.75,0:43:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼资金直接投入“国际屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Corleone's capital invested directly into International Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.65,0:43:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家古老而受尊敬的欧洲公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}an old and respected European company.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.80,0:43:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但迈克尔·柯利昂尼有一项雄心勃勃的计划\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But Michael Corleone has an ambitious program
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.56,0:43:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要将这家房地产股份公司扩展为…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to expand this real estate holding company
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.40,0:43:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家跨国企业集团，从而能…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}into an international conglomerate that can...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.90,0:43:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不是靠政治意识形态，而是靠东部的高效技术\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...no by political ideologies, but by Eastern techniques of efficiency
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.14,0:43:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 专注，以及不受限制的…  - 柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-and focus and unlimited... -Mr. Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生，请原谅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.80,0:43:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你是否将两亿美元存入梵蒂冈银行？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Isn't it true that you recently deposited $200 million in the Vatican Bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.65,0:43:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该银行隶属“国际屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which is affiliated with International Immobiliare?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.83,0:43:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的，有何不可？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is true. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.45,0:43:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次特定的存款在时机上是不是有些疑问？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wasn't there any questioning about the timing on this particular deposit
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.85,0:44:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者，有些说法说…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}or wasn't there some talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 主席先生，容我发言  - …事实上…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Mr. Chairman, if I may? - ...the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.73,0:44:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·安东里尼·柯利昂尼基金会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vito Andolino Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.32,0:44:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生的女儿玛丽是其主席\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}of which Mr. Corleone's daughter Mary is chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.35,0:44:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经设立了总数为1亿美元的捐款\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has established an endowment in the amount of one hundred million dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔钱来自他本人的家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The money comes from his own family,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.15,0:44:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将由梵蒂冈管理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and will be administered by the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.41,0:44:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这解答了你的问题了吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Answer your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.03,0:44:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一向相信…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have always believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.03,0:44:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助你的同伴，是有益的，从各方面来说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}helping your fellow man is profitable, in every sense
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.92,0:44:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利人利己\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}personally and bottom-line.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.92,0:44:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位股东同仁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My fellow shareholders
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.02,0:44:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果欧洲和美国能学习一起合作\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if Europe and America can learn to cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.63,0:44:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能学会汇聚我们的财富，分享我们的市场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if we can learn to pool our wealth, share our markets
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.93,0:44:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能在世界任何地方 打败任何竞争对手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we can defeat any competition anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.44,0:44:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谢谢各位今天给我的机会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me thank you for the time you've given me here today
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.35,0:44:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位能善待本人的提案  谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I hope that you will look favorably on my proposal. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.10,0:45:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把麦克风给我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, let me at this microphone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.23,0:45:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么能让这样一个罪犯掌管我们公司？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can we let a criminal like thar run our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.95,0:45:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他一脸西西里匪相，你们看不到吗？  - 秩序\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-He's got the map of Sicily on his face. Can't you see it? -Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.92,0:45:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秩序\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.83,0:45:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是天主教徒就是个黑手党，要我说…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's either Catholic or mafioso. And I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.67,0:45:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿投资集团不能支持这项提案\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Hamilton Investors Group cannot support this proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.90,0:45:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大主教阁下？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.45,0:45:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.60,0:45:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈银行感觉…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Vatican Bank feels
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.34,0:45:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际屹莫比公司…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that International Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.65,0:45:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柯利昂尼先生手中 将会是安全的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}will be safe in Mr. Corleone's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.33,0:45:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审核及最终批准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Subject to audit and final ratification
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.14,0:45:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须在罗马做出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which must take place in Rome
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.43,0:45:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请与本席一同欢迎迈克尔·柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}please join me in welcoming Mr. Michael Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.47,0:45:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.36,0:46:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼说我是基金会的门面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tony says that I'm a front for the foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.31,0:46:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你利用我只是为了操控\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that you're using me just to pull the strings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.12,0:46:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得自己想要的利益\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to get the money where you want it。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.55,0:46:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，拜托\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.42,0:46:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了擦亮你的公众形象\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To shine up your public image
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.80,0:46:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.68,0:46:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，这是真的，这个基金会，它是真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, this is real, this foundation. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.13,0:46:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前想要安东尼加入\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted Anthony to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.44,0:46:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要你们两个一起来做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I wanted two of you would be together on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.25,0:46:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会干涉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.31,0:46:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有要求我才会帮手  - 但是…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I'll help only if you ask. -But...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.61,0:46:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这么做真正是为了什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But what is this really for?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.71,0:46:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这件事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.61,0:46:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要做这件事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.65,0:46:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做这件事是为了我的孩子们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm doing this for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.72,0:46:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是为你的孩子们做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're doing it for your children too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.28,0:46:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个基金会应该帮助所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This foundation is supposed to help all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.55,0:46:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，这是宗旨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course. That's the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.00,0:46:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是合法的，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is legitimate, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.76,0:46:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓这是合法的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear this is legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.85,0:47:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸，我想要这件事带我更亲近你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dad, I want this to bring me closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.23,0:47:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甘受地狱之火\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would burn in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.68,0:47:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保护你安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.18,0:47:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不，你去上另一辆车，我搭迈克尔的车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no. You go in the other car. I'll ride with Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.03,0:47:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你家族最老的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As your family's oldest friend
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.61,0:47:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是被选中给你传信\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm always chosen to bring you messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.30,0:47:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧，唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell me, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.18,0:48:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的老伙伴们 都感激你过去给他们赚的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your old partners are grateful for the money you made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.14,0:48:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…他们崇拜你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They...they worship you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.32,0:48:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在他们很伤心，因为他们认为你抛弃了他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But their hearts are broken because they think you abandoned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.25,0:48:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要分享你跟“屹莫比”的交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They want to share your deal on Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.80,0:48:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次成为一家人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to be a family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.72,0:48:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能洗干净他们的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It can purify their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.55,0:48:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不能做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.06,0:48:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”必须是合法的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare must be legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.03,0:48:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.65,0:48:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他们不高兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But they're unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.12,0:48:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.00,0:48:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己别无所求\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I ask nothing for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.06,0:48:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能安度晚年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only peace in my old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.22,0:48:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我得抚慰身边的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I must please the world around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.55,0:49:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你父亲是个讲道理的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, your father was a reasonable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.00,0:49:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他学学吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.00,0:49:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从我父亲那里学了许多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I learned many things from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.71,0:49:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集一次会议吧，我的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Call a meeting, my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.14,0:49:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会有亏欠，或怨恨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so there are no debts or grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.54,0:49:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将创造和平\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We will make the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.30,0:49:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.10,0:49:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈今天宣称{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vatican announced today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.63,0:49:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇保禄六世已因病…{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that Pope Paul VI has canceled his Sunday blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.64,0:49:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取消周日祈福{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}due to ill health.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.64,0:49:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的医生已下令完全卧床休息{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His physician has ordered total bed rest
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.81,0:49:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并终止一切活动{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and cessation of all activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.25,0:50:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们刚开了个记者会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They just had a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.46,0:50:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说教皇的情况危重，原话是“gravissimo”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They said the pope's condition is grave. gravissimo, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.95,0:50:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次会议的目的在于批准…{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The purpose of this meeting is to ratify
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.49,0:50:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们纽约各股东通过的动议{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the motion passed by our shareholders in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.20,0:50:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.45,0:50:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本集团代表天主教商人财团\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}our group represents a consortium of Catholic businessmen
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.15,0:50:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对柯利昂尼掌权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}against the Corleone control.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.90,0:50:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈已经投票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vatican has cast its vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.44,0:51:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼集团已经控制了董事会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Corleone Group already controls the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.36,0:51:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据拉特兰条约 梵蒂冈的投票必须在这里获准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}According to the Lateran Treaty the Vatican's vote must be ratified here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.90,0:51:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在罗马这里，由教皇批准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here in Rome by the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.24,0:51:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇，病情危重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope is gravely ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.75,0:51:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他康复之前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Until he recovers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.22,0:51:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无能为力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.59,0:51:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他死了呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What if he dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.80,0:51:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，如你们美国人所说的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then as you Americans say
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.13,0:51:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一笔勾消\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All bets are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.03,0:51:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们，拜托\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gentlemen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.27,0:51:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个短暂耽搁，没别的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a brief delay, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.68,0:51:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下  诸位\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Excellency, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.35,0:51:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议你们加入大家一起祷告\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I advise you join us in our prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.15,0:51:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求圣父早日康复\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for the Holy Father's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.22,0:51:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有过共识\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now, we had an agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.06,0:51:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场会议最多是个形式，如此而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This meeting was to be merely a formality. That's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.03,0:52:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 请坐下  - 我宁可站着  能不能有谁给我一个答案？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Please sit down. -I'd rather stand. Could someone juset give me an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.57,0:52:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把自己置于前线了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have put ourselves on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.40,0:52:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”在欧洲传统上根深蒂固\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Immobiliare has its roots in the European tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.35,0:52:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽量理解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.85,0:52:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.45,0:52:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们手段卑劣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your tactics are despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.26,0:52:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，这可是个挺大的指控，来自一位柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, that's quite an indictment, coming from a Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.56,0:52:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们 先生们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.78,0:52:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住你们是在梵蒂冈，拜托\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember you're in the Vatican. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.85,0:52:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要的，是什么东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.16,0:52:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，你可以取得控制权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes. You will take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.35,0:52:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很高兴由你来为我们的小船队掌舵\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We'll gladly put you at the helm of our little fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.50,0:52:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们的船只，必须全体往一个方向航行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but our ships must all sail in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.93,0:52:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.52,0:52:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说得好 你会跟我们一起待多久？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}who can say how long your stay with us will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.68,0:52:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是针对你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.98,0:52:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's only business.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.01,0:52:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该懂，教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You should know, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.69,0:53:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.33,0:53:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要跟我做生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You want to do business with me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.20,0:53:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就跟你们做生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will do business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.65,0:53:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒蛇，他们全是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vipers, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.54,0:53:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回到波吉亚家族时代了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're back with the Borgias.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.34,0:53:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔叔叔  - 安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Uncle Michael. -Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.41,0:53:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你来了，见到你太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I heard you were here. It's so nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.51,0:53:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森  - 你好吗，安德鲁？  - 太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent. -How are you, Andrew? -It's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.35,0:53:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟波吉亚家族有何关系？那种日子过去了，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, what is this with the Borgias? Those days are over, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.13,0:53:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认得吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.83,0:53:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.90,0:53:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚科橄榄油\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Genco Olive Oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.80,0:53:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们祖父开端的地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's where our grandfather got his start.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.63,0:53:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当递送员起家，每周挣3块\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he start as a delivery boy making three bucks a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.10,0:53:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3年后他拥有了这家公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Three years later, he owned the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.55,0:53:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国才有这种事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.64,0:53:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.79,0:53:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，文森佐，你躲到哪儿去了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo, where have you been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.19,0:53:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抛下我们…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You deserted us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.55,0:53:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是我们最需要你帮忙的时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}when we need your help so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.06,0:53:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我回来了，我能为你们做什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well now I'm back, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.43,0:53:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉乔·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Get rid of Joe Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.83,0:54:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他卖毒品给孩子们  - 你看，我还是姑娘的时候，事情不一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-He sells drugs to children. -You know, when I was a girl, it was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.12,0:54:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我变老了，倒害怕夜里在街上走路了，知道吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm an older woman, I'm afraid to walk the streets at night, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.04,0:54:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们大概在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where are they supposed to be at?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.44,0:54:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢，怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lou, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.84,0:54:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经迟了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.78,0:54:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候让你失望过？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have I ever let you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.81,0:54:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.25,0:54:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.41,0:54:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太谢谢你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.85,0:54:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们愉快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.09,0:54:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.53,0:54:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居有些麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Neighborhood's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.06,0:54:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都这么照应他们吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're keeping your eye out for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.62,0:54:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.85,0:54:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.57,0:54:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}From now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.77,0:54:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以来都想念你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.24,0:54:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想念你，堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed you, too, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.84,0:54:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀念跟堂表兄妹们一起长大\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed growing up with all my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.84,0:54:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时不认识你，我就想念你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I didn't know you, and I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.85,0:54:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得我们父亲的事吗？过去的日子？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you remember stories about our fathers, the old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.58,0:54:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得，你想知道什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah. What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.26,0:55:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑尼是怎么样的人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was Sonny like?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.23,0:55:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是城里的王子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He was the prince of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.06,0:55:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在我出生之前就死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He died before I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.70,0:55:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我听过关于他的许多故事  他是个传奇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I heard a million stories. He was a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.53,0:55:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我父亲呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.84,0:55:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个伟大的人物，你父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A great man, your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.74,0:55:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个英雄，他拯救了家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a hero. He saved the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.98,0:55:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森  - 什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.75,0:55:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有没有杀死自己的亲兄弟？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did he kill his own brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.52,0:55:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.36,0:55:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那些都是谎话？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So those are all lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.36,0:55:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些故事，亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just stories, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.90,0:55:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.63,0:55:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.64,0:55:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.51,0:55:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你我身边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴你在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.55,0:56:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂妹{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cugina.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.32,0:56:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.13,0:56:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带乔伊·札萨来搭个机，然后把他推下去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd like to take Joey Zasa up for a ride in this and drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.87,0:56:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨什么都不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.74,0:56:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个微不足道的跑腿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a small-time enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.14,0:56:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他诈唬、威胁，但什么也不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He bluffs, threats, but nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.05,0:56:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔着一英里你就能看见他来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'll be able to see him coming a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.38,0:56:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们应该杀了他，趁他还没…  - 不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We should kill him before he kills... -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.12,0:56:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不要恨你的敌人，这会影响你的判断\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Never hate your enemies. It affects your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.68,0:56:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.73,0:57:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴再次见到你，柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening. Nice to see you again, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.99,0:57:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们信任你，掌管我们赌场的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We trusted you to manage our money in the casinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.39,0:57:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年都不到，你卖掉了那些赌场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not even 20 years you sold the casinos
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.06,0:57:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们大家赚了大钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and you made fortunes for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.30,0:57:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害啊  唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bravo, Don Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.90,0:57:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.95,0:58:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  我到这里来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Friends, I have come here
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.45,0:58:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}because
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.25,0:58:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们共同的事业已经结束了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}our business together is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.37,0:58:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经兴盛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have prospered
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.25,0:58:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and now it is time for us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.50,0:58:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除我们之间的业务关系了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to dissolve the business relationship between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.42,0:58:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.19,0:58:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我的确有点小惊喜  艾尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I do have a little surprise, Al
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.56,0:58:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位在赌场的股份\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your shares in the casino
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.40,0:58:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我应该省掉所有繁文缛节\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought I'd cut through all the red tape
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.21,0:58:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们直接拿到你们的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so you can get your money right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.74,0:58:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五千万\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}$50 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.31,0:58:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每个人都一样，取决于多少…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Not everybody gets the same. It depends on how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.31,0:58:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没你的份儿  - …是你投资的，以及多长时间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Nothing for you. -you invested and how long for.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.08,0:58:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，这真的很大方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, this is really generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.35,0:58:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，好极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.06,0:58:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazier
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.33,0:58:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，巴利西，你当初投了多少？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Parisi, how much did you invest?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.80,0:58:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记不得了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.80,0:59:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，上帝会保佑你的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, you're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.47,0:59:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家族做了大部分苦差事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My family has done much of the hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.00,0:59:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担了很多风险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}taken many risks
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.41,0:59:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了给其他家族挣钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all to make money for the rest of the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.85,0:59:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都认识乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You all know Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.89,0:59:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认他是个重要人物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He is, I admit, an important man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.45,0:59:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的照片上了纽约时报杂志封面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His picture is on the cover of the New York Times Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.79,0:59:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他获得了绅士杂志的最佳黑帮着装奖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He gets the Esquire magazine award for the best-dressed gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.10,0:59:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸都赞扬他 因为他雇用黑人加入家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The newspapers praise him because he hires blacks into his family
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.10,0:59:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这显示了他有善心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which shows he has a good heart
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.17,0:59:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个名人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.37,0:59:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.41,0:59:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有一天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe one day
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.38,0:59:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会让你们大家都受欢迎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he will make all of you popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.52,0:59:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.79,1:00:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更讲究外表\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I make more of a bella figura.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.72,1:00:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的天性\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That is my nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.59,1:00:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也想向合法企业迈进一步\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I also want to make a move into legitimate enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.73,1:00:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢从教皇那里弄个小别针\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd like to get a little pin from the pope.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.90,1:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，我接纳黑人及西班牙裔进入我的家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sure, I take the blacks and the Spanish into my family
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.05,1:00:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…这就是美国\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}because that's America.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.22,1:00:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担保他们不在这些街区贩毒？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you guarantee that they don't deal drugs in those neighborhoods.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.42,1:00:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不担保\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.55,1:00:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担保我会杀了这么干的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guarantee I'll kill anybody who does.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.79,1:00:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟他谈谈，让我跟他谈谈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me talk to him. Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.19,1:00:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能拒绝唐·阿尔托贝洛？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who can refuse Don Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.50,1:00:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，你…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey, hey you...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.90,1:00:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.47,1:00:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你们所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I say to all of you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.67,1:00:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天没有被尊重对待\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have been treated this day with no respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.00,1:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你们所有人赚过钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've earned you all money.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.12,1:00:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你们发了财\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've made you rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.00,1:00:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只要求少许\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I asked for little.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.51,1:00:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你们不给？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. You will not give?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.31,1:01:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会来拿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll take.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.82,1:01:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于唐·柯利昂尼…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As for Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，他今天讲得…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}well he makes it...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.72,1:01:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说很清楚，他是我的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}very clear to me today that he is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.33,1:01:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们必须在我俩当中做选择\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You must choose between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.03,1:01:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，不要，乔伊，不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey Joey， no， Joey， no， Joey
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.18,1:01:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以一起讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We can reason together.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.14,1:01:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.08,1:01:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，迈克尔，拜托…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, Michael, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.98,1:01:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们来协商，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}let's agree, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.52,1:01:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不知道自己在说…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He doesn't know what he's...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.02,1:01:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.39,1:01:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，迈克尔，消息到处都是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, Michael, Michael. The news is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.16,1:01:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都在说，你已经控制了“屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everyone is saying that, you control Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.43,1:01:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”已经在秘鲁洗黑钱了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare already is laundering money in Peru
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.05,1:01:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有拿骚  我们都知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and Nassau. We know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.67,1:01:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔 我们朋友也做了四十年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen to me. We've been friends for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.25,1:02:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也应该沾一点光\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We should wet our beaks a little, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.54,1:02:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想和你一起做生意，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We want to do business with you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.88,1:02:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对啊  - 用圣水洗净我们的钱...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-That's right... -We can wash our money clean in the holy water of...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.10,1:02:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.19,1:02:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是暗杀，快走，跟我来  - 咱们离开这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-It's a hit. Let's go. Follow me. -Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.45,1:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的外套  - 别管你的外套了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-My coat! -Forget your coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.15,1:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的幸运外套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my lucky coat!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.37,1:02:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的幸运外套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my lucky coat!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.66,1:02:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在我后面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Stay right behind me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.20,1:03:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基，走这边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mikey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.72,1:03:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札萨  你这狗娘养的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Zasa you son of bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.21,1:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，我们离开这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, we're outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.75,1:04:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你干得好，文森  - 谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You did good, Vincen. -Grazier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.30,1:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老的唐都差不多被扫清了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The old Dons were pretty much wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.65,1:04:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存下来的跟乔伊·札萨做了交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The ones that survived made deals with Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.09,1:04:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.36,1:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他活下来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.69,1:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在斯达坦岛跟他女儿一起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's with his daughters now in Staten Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.56,1:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他要退隐，回西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Says he's gonna retire to Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.40,1:04:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人撑腰，乔·札萨绝对来不了这一手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa would never pull something like this without the backing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.70,1:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是个打手，是个跑腿的，他什么也不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's just muscle. He's an enforcer. He's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.11,1:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没那个才智搞直升机攻击\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He doesn't have the wit for that helicopter attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.56,1:04:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至没有那个野心消灭整个委员会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He doesn't even have the ambition to wipe out the whole commission.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.03,1:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我说我们得反击，干掉札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I say we hit back and take Zasa out!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.48,1:05:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远别让任何人知道你在想什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Never let anyone know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.47,1:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们…我们传话给乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, let's get a...let's get a message to Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.67,1:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敬重他所做的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I respect what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.11,1:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后浪推前浪，这是自然规律\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The new overthrows the old. It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.55,1:05:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能跟这个人做生意？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can you do business with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.48,1:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个生意人，这是首先第一位的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm a businessman, first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.18,1:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟他进一步冲突\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want no further conflict with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.83,1:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他，我决定他是死是活\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You tell him from me that he can live or he can die.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.39,1:05:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特，你闭不闭嘴？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, will you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.73,1:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.38,1:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.45,1:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能是单独干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He can't be doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.62,1:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我以为我退出的时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just when I thought I was out,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.93,1:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我拖回去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they pull me back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.54,1:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真正的敌人，还没露出他的面孔呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our true enemy has not yet shown his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.38,1:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.80,1:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.62,1:06:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带着他的药没有？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Has he taken his medicine?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.46,1:06:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他吃什么药\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know what he took.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.10,1:06:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能喘气了  - 快叫医生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I've got my wind back. -Call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.54,1:06:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能喘气了  - 好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I've got my wind back. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.00,1:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快去  快去!  - 文森特\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Run, run! -Vincent!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.34,1:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔向雷电  雷声伤不了人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Run at thunderbolt. Thunder can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.15,1:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无害的声音而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Harmless noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.85,1:07:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.50,1:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你他妈虚伪的老东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You deceitful old fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.41,1:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔托贝洛，你他妈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Altobello, you fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.92,1:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.09,1:07:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.41,1:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，天啊，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God. Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.22,1:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳驾\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.62,1:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让一让\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Clear please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.72,1:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通知凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll call Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.87,1:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好，先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.80,1:08:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能不能在这里停一下？几分钟就回来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can we wait here? We'll be back in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.64,1:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.44,1:08:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里森先生，你说是急事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Harrison, you said it was urgent.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.57,1:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来告解你的罪过吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have you come to confess your sins?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.15,1:08:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼糖尿病中风\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael Corleone suffered a diabetic stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.45,1:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你应该在见报前知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought you should know that before you read it in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.46,1:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.44,1:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在病危昏迷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's in a coma on the critical list.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.69,1:08:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来强调交易不论任何情形都将继续\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm here to insist the deal goes through in any event.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.56,1:08:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇不剩多少时间了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope has not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.23,1:08:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，跟你一样，我处在一个困难的位置上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, as you, I am in a difficult position.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.37,1:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得尽快争取核准此交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have to ratify this deal as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.51,1:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我们有共识\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.35,1:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.68,1:08:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去医院\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.77,1:08:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为柯利昂尼先生祈祷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll pray for Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.80,1:08:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.13,1:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与柯利昂尼先生同在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our thoughts are with Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.87,1:08:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你，吉姆神父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you, Father Jim.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.69,1:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果柯利昂尼死了，一切会被揭开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everything will be out in the open if Corleone dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.66,1:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求时间吧，凯恩济格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pray for time, Keinszig.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.43,1:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个习惯源自…对永恒的长久思考\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A habit born of, a long contemplation of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.85,1:09:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧，文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just forget about it, Vinnie
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.22,1:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？我干嘛要算了？不过是简单的暗杀而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why? Why would I forget about it? It's a simple hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.78,1:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，我很乐意打击乔伊·札萨，干掉那娘炮，懂吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look, I'd love to smack Joey Zasa then whack the fag, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.03,1:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是不可能的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.12,1:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总是混在人群里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's always mingling with people
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.02,1:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在电视镜头前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in front of TV cameras
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.53,1:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己的地盘上，这是不可能的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in his own neighborhood. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.76,1:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不是不可能的，我们办得到  - 怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-It's not impossible. It'll work for us.　-How?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.43,1:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为他会让迈克尔叔叔活下去？换了你会吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You think he's gonna let Uncle Michael survive this thing? Would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.51,1:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也可能一病不起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He may not survive anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.85,1:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备怎么下手？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.77,1:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做，我会亲自动手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd do it. I'd do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.28,1:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.14,1:09:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你需要什么？  - 你看能不能派几个人给我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-What would you need? -See if you can get me a couple guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.92,1:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hello, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.76,1:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.36,1:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.03,1:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再没想到你会来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I never expected you to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.85,1:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我知道，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.58,1:10:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.05,1:10:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.21,1:10:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.68,1:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一次看到你样子这么无助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}this is the first time I've seen you look so helpless.
