Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.57,1:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你病得越重越聪明，嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The sicker you get, the wiser you get, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.00,1:11:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我死的时候会极其聪明\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I'm dead, I'm gonna be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.75,1:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔  - 怎么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Michael -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.21,1:11:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要替托尼谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want to thank you for Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.23,1:11:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做得很好，他真的受到一些正面关注\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's doing really well. He's gotten some very good notices
