Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.22,1:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.86,1:11:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.70,1:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是光荣，在西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's a real honor. In Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.92,1:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去的  我不会错过的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will be there. I won't miss that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.86,1:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会错过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't miss that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.70,1:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.55,1:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go see dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.96,1:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，来，过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, come, come here.
