Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.90,1:12:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.93,1:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你怎么样，爸爸？  - 过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-How you doin' pop? -Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.34,1:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈告诉我了  你演出的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your mother told me. She told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.30,1:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴勒莫的事？我真希望你能去，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}About Palermo? I really wanted you to be there, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.85,1:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  过来亲我一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course. Come here, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.86,1:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼堂哥？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cousin Vinnie?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.01,1:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，他不在这里，要不你打他公寓电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, he isn't here. Why don't you call his apartment
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.79,1:13:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他留个电话录音\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}leave a message on his machine?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.21,1:13:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你堂妹玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your cousin, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.54,1:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.11,1:13:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.47,1:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, cuz
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.32,1:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得应该顺路来一下，可以吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just thought I'd drop by. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.60,1:13:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫弟兄们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna get the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.52,1:13:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，这不好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, it's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.30,1:13:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该来的，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You shouldn't have come, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.26,1:13:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能几分钟，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A couple minutes only, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.98,1:13:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你样子很漂亮，表妹  - 谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You look beautiful, cous. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.94,1:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的俱乐部，你的藏身处？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So this is your club, your hideout?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.35,1:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.76,1:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.97,1:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很奇怪，只有我和康妮姑姑在屋里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's so strange, just me and Aunt Connie in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.16,1:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你在一起我感觉好多了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I feel better when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.25,1:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了，亲爱的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's wrong, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.04,1:13:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的被我父亲的事吓着了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm really scared about my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.97,1:13:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.04,1:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我看到他们把他抬出救护车时  我以为他死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I saw them take him out of that ambulance, I thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.85,1:14:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道，人人都说他会好起来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know. Everybody says he's gonna be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.60,1:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.75,1:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我小时候他们扫射我们家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I remember them shooting at our house when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.77,1:14:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔·奈利有一次带了另外一些保镖来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And Al Neri came one time with other bodyguards
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.72,1:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我和托尼带走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and just took me and Tony away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.58,1:14:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是这一套又发生了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is it all happening again?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.17,1:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那不一样，亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not like that, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.99,1:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么躲在这里？有什么事会对你不利吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then why are you hiding here? Is something going to happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.60,1:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事的，表亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nothing's gonna happen to me, cugina.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.28,1:14:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会照顾你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.76,1:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跟你一起躲在这里吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I stay here and hide out with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.79,1:14:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你得为小伙子们做gnocchi团子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have to make gnocchi for the boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.30,1:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不懂怎么做菜，不过我可以帮忙\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know I don't know how to cook, but I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.95,1:15:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.25,1:15:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.25,1:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, cuz
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.44,1:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你  堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, too, cuz.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.96,1:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，做饭吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, let's cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.37,1:16:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.65,1:16:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些媒体人、警察…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the people like you in the press, the police...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.73,1:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱用“黑手党” “我们的事业”这种词\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}use words like Mafia, Cosa Nostra.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.53,1:16:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是幻想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.22,1:16:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们意裔美国人是了不起的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Italian-Americans are great people.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.45,1:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们铺下建设这城市的砖块，我们中有艺术家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We laid the bricks that built this city. We have the artists.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.90,1:17:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有梅乌奇，他发明了电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have Meucci. He invented the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.85,1:17:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有唐·阿米奇，他扮演了发明电话的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have Don Ameche who played the guy who invented the telephone. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.72,1:17:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以听好了，赶紧给自己买张抽奖券\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, listen, come on, buy yourself a nice raffle ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.92,1:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没准给自己赢一辆凯迪拉克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe win yourself a Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.16,1:17:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这香肠棒极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The salciccia is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.81,1:17:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给，吃个三明治吧，我们走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here, have a sandwich. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.69,1:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 见到你真好，札萨先生  - 祝你愉快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Nice to see you, Mr. Zasa. -Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.86,1:17:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了去买抽奖券  嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't forget to buy your raffle tickets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.93,1:17:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你干什么？  - 他不是故意的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-What are you doin'?  -He didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.43,1:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  快过来，孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's sorry. Come here, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.60,1:17:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK, OK, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.42,1:18:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，你好吗，朋友？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey, how are you, pal?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.76,1:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，你好吗，哥们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, how are you, Buddy Boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.86,1:18:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey Zasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.66,1:18:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，操你屁股\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey! Up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.90,1:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁？你认识他？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who is this? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.00,1:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别理他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.20,1:18:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，谁会赢这辆汽车？“蚂蚁”吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey,Joey, who's gonna win the car? The Ant?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.32,1:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意裔美国人的坏名声就是这样来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is the thing that gives the Italian-Americans a bad name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.21,1:18:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种败类\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A caponi like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.55,1:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，操你屁股\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey, up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.53,1:18:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你他妈下不下车？你有抽奖券吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, would you get off of that fuckin' car, all right? You got a raffle ticket?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.09,1:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，看看我的抽奖券，开始喽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey, take a good look at my raffle ticket, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.73,1:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要这样对待你，和你的抽奖券\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here's what I think of you and your raffle ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.13,1:18:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你，快他妈离开这车，我要捏烂你他妈的蛋蛋\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I told you, get the fuck outta this car, I'll break your fucking balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.18,1:18:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你他妈的滚开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.13,1:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开，滚开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Get outta here. Get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.46,1:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯库里亚诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Squigliaro.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还跑，乔，你这坨屎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Run, Joey, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.73,1:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门  快开门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Open the door! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.74,1:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，乔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.83,1:19:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.49,1:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不准下这种命令\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't ever again give that kind of order.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.85,1:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我活着就不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not while I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.67,1:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.94,1:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你病得不能做决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were too sick to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.40,1:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我征得奈利同意，我征得康妮同意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I got a go-ahead from Neri, I got a go-ahead from Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.16,1:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.05,1:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正确的决定，迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the right decision, Uncle Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.62,1:20:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是错误的决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.72,1:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我指挥这个家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I command this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.93,1:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.85,1:20:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我想要的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it was not what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.25,1:20:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明不明白？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.96,1:20:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.57,1:21:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.02,1:21:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.59,1:21:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  文森特  扶我回床上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. Vincent, help me to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.53,1:21:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你谈谈，单独，就一会儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanna talk to you, alone, for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.77,1:21:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.63,1:21:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是觉得对你负有责任\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always felt responsible for you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.73,1:21:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know than...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.15,1:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your father
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.00,1:21:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥 我们个性相反\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}my brother, we were opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.80,1:21:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会吵架争辩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We would fight and argue
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.24,1:21:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从未怀疑过他的爱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I never doubted his love.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.89,1:21:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他愿意为我做任何事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He would do anything for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.17,1:21:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的脾气\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But his temper
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.00,1:22:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太急躁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it was too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.40,1:22:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮蔽了他的理智\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Clouded his reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.37,1:22:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想要你犯这种错误\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't want you to make that mistake
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.85,1:22:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Also
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.15,1:22:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对女人也很有一套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he, too, had a way with women.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.61,1:22:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特…  - 我也这么听说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent.. -So I hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.51,1:22:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我女儿是在做什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what are you doing with my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.49,1:22:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她是怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you doing with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.13,1:22:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.34,1:22:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.11,1:22:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.72,1:23:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.23,1:23:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们动手时…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When they come
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.56,1:23:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会冲着你所爱的来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they'll come at what you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.68,1:23:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你应该换一种生活了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, you must lead another life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.25,1:23:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人所能要求的你都拥有了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have everything a man could desire.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.55,1:23:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是时候退休了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's time for you to retire.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.45,1:23:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有太多责任了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have too much responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.23,1:23:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- “屹莫比”？  - 是的{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Immobiliare? -Si.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.64,1:23:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在太困难，你真应该退出来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Too difficult now. You should really get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.12,1:23:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解不了解…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you know about...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.73,1:23:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些意大利的大佬？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}those pezzonovante in Italy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.70,1:23:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年纪太老，对那些新人一无所知\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm too old to know anything about those new people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.80,1:23:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须服老了，回家种橄榄树和西红柿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I must accept my age and grow my olives and tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.63,1:24:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没那么老\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're not that old
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.71,1:24:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的病很重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But you're very ill.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.43,1:24:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.95,1:24:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看能做什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me see what can be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.60,1:24:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我努力把你的路铺容易一点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me work to make your path a little easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.00,1:24:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的友谊一向有此作用\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your friendship does that always.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.67,1:24:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就高兴了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.77,1:24:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨，你看错他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joe Zasa, You were wrong about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.11,1:24:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太信任人，这一直是我的错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trust too much. That's always been my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.39,1:24:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.26,1:24:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变节叛变到处都有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Treachery is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.60,1:24:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你依然能牵动，即使是现在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You still have your fingers on the strings, even now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.17,1:24:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要多见面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's see more of each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.20,1:24:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.01,1:24:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西西里见？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In Sicily?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.77,1:24:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.54,1:24:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西西里{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In Sicilia.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.78,1:24:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西西里{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In Sicilia.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.43,1:25:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.90,1:25:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·本蒂诺，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Bendino, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.23,1:26:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你们来这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted to bring you here
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.03,1:26:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让我的老朋友及庇护人唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so that my old friend and protector Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.90,1:26:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们出主意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}could advise us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.10,1:26:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·汤马西诺，你对阿尔托贝洛有什么看法？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Tommasino, what do you think about Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.31,1:26:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很有才干的人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A very talented man.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.51,1:26:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他维持了我们西西里人与美国朋友之间的和平{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He has kept the peace between our Sicilian and American friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.45,1:26:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲道理的圣人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The saint of reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.97,1:26:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特兰大城那次大屠杀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The bloodbath in Atlantic City,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.43,1:26:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给纽约留下个烂摊子，现在…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}left New York a mess. Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.93,1:26:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨起码曾经经营得有个样子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa at least was running a very tight ship,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.73,1:27:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他出局了，我们有义务介入\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but now that he's out of the picture, we're obligated to step in.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.50,1:27:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入回去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Step back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.34,1:27:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不介入，中国人、哥伦比亚人就会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we don't, the Chinese, the Colombians will.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.34,1:27:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家族从不贩毒{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Corleone's left drugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.47,1:27:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以纽约弱，巴勒莫强{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so New York is weak, and Palermo is strong
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.95,1:27:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的敌人总是会在你丢下的地方坐大{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your enemies always get strong on what you leave behind
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.42,1:27:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.62,1:27:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁可能下令那场屠杀{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}who could give the order for that massacre
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.13,1:27:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时还能施压梵蒂冈的交易？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and still pressure the Vatican deal?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.14,1:27:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有卢凯西…{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.33,1:27:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,势力范围能达这两地{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}can reach between these two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.13,1:27:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的船必须朝同一个方向航行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our ships must all sail in the same direction
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.21,1:27:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利政界几个世纪来都有这种人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Italian politics have had these kind of men for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.56,1:27:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们，是真正的黑手党\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're, the true Mafia
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.15,1:27:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教和梵蒂冈银行，才是大问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Archbishop and the Vatican bank, that's the big problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.60,1:27:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们同一个问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're the same problem
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.32,1:27:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BJ，他们有勾结\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}B.J., they're connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.53,1:27:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教有一些很有权势的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Archbishop has very powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.96,1:28:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全力保护他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They totally protect him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.87,1:28:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会方面有没有我们能投靠的人？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is there someone in the church we can turn to?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.80,1:28:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把我们的问题告诉这个人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Someone we can tell our problem to.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.34,1:28:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢机主教龙巴度{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cardinal Lamberto.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.64,1:28:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为人睿智和善{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A wise and good man
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.38,1:28:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极有影响力{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}very influential.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.31,1:28:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会见你的{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He will see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.03,1:28:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bene.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.30,1:28:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去见这位枢机主教龙巴度\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will go see this Cardinal Lamberto
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.19,1:28:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们能不能用文明的方式解决问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and see if we can work things out in a civilized way
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.87,1:28:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遵守协约\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You honor your agreements
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.14,1:28:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对付的这些人是无赖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These people you're dealing with are crooks
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.40,1:28:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不讲信义\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they have no honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.61,1:28:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话是最终决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My word is final.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.95,1:29:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治与犯罪，它们是一回事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Politics and crime. They're the same thing
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.61,1:29:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩 精彩 精彩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bravo! Bravo, Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.48,1:29:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请你们大家到此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have invited you all here
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.81,1:29:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝我的儿子首次歌剧院演出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to celebrate, my son's first appearance in an opera house
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.75,1:29:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们玩“费城牌”  - 他将于三周后…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- We'll play "Philadelphia" - He will be appearing, in about three weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.82,1:29:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 7张牌，2张下，4张上…  - 在玛西摩剧院登台\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- 7 cards. 2 down, 4 up  -in the Theatre Maximo
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.50,1:29:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演出歌剧“乡间骑士”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in the opera, Cavalleria Rusticana.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.96,1:29:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乡间骑士，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Cavalleria Rusticana dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.83,1:29:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士  看来我买错歌剧票了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cavalleria. I think I've got tickets to the wrong opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.87,1:29:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在纽约待得太久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been in New York too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.40,1:29:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，大家都会收到门票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anyway, you will all receive tickets.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.00,1:29:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多捧场啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So come on down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.64,1:29:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  我有一份礼物给你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, dad, I've got a present for you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.75,1:30:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它来自柯利昂尼小镇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It comes from the town of Corleone and uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.18,1:30:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一首真正的西西里歌谣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's authentic Sicilian
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.32,1:30:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.32,1:30:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为你学的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I learned it for you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.00,1:30:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}月在空中烧 我在爱中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.90,1:30:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}火焰殆尽 正如我心
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.36,1:30:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}我的灵魂呼喊于痛苦中
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.67,1:30:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}无法平静 多么可怕的夜
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.53,1:30:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}时光消逝 但日子不再来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.25,1:30:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}太阳不再有 只因她没有归来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.27,1:31:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}燃烧我的土地 燃烧我的心
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.65,1:31:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}她渴求清水 而我渴求爱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.95,1:31:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}我能向谁吟唱我的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.26,1:31:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}阳台上已然无人现身
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.20,1:31:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又漂亮又善良  我爱过她\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She was, wonderful, beautiful. I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.42,1:31:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而她死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.82,1:31:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的亲信保镖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My trusted bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.26,1:31:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我车上装了炸弹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}planted a bomb in my car
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.56,1:31:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在我之前去开车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}she drove it before I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.23,1:32:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么美丽的地方如此暴力？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why is such a beautiful country, so violent?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.93,1:32:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}History.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.52,1:32:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，妈妈跟我说起从前…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, mom was telling me about the old days,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.63,1:32:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最担心的只是考试不及格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}when her biggest worry was just passing exams
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.24,1:32:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，那时候是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes it was, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.24,1:32:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我为你担心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I worry about you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.06,1:32:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.81,1:32:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，你真是个暖心的孩子，你一向如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary you're such a warm-hearted girl, you always were.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.50,1:32:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱我的家人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.59,1:32:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是你的堂兄文森？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even your cousin Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.98,1:32:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心爱他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.56,1:32:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的近亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's your first cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.28,1:32:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我更得爱他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then I love him first.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.83,1:32:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，你不能见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, you can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.34,1:32:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再见他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just don't see him any more
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.50,1:32:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的对  这太危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's right. it's too dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.28,1:32:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，听我说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.46,1:32:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能再见他了，不能以那种方式\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You can't see him anymore. Not in that fashion.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.92,1:32:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.48,1:32:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你，跟我保证\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please promise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.16,1:32:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.76,1:32:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事得服从我，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Obey me on this Mary!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.31,1:32:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.68,1:33:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽是个聪明人，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary's smart, dad
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.28,1:33:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最终会理解的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}she'll understand eventually.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.02,1:33:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的堂妹，我的宝贝{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bella cugina...Tesoro mio.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.18,1:33:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要见我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.41,1:33:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.38,1:33:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要你为我办件事  - 好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I want you to do something for me. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.76,1:33:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.58,1:33:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.96,1:33:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入，你需要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm in. What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.58,1:33:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你出卖灵魂给唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to sell your soul to Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.29,1:34:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To betray me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.63,1:34:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他永远不会相信我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He'll never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.75,1:34:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.59,1:34:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那要看情形  - 坐下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-That depends. -Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.13,1:34:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.14,1:34:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能不能弄清 阿尔托贝洛的关系有多高层\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}See if you can learn how high Altobello is connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.88,1:34:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排一次见面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Arrange a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.12,1:34:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你对我多么忠心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You say how devoted you are to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.58,1:34:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他你的问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell him your problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.82,1:34:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向他求助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ask for his help.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.00,1:34:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么问题？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.71,1:34:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你想和我女儿私奔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That you want to run away with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.20,1:34:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你知道如果这么做了，我就成了你的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only you know that if you do, I will become your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.21,1:34:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我绝不会做那种事，迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know I'd never do that, Uncle Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.71,1:34:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.98,1:35:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你求阿尔托贝洛来找我谈 以成就你们的婚姻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ask Altobello to speak to me. To further the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.95,1:35:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你们毕竟是堂兄妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But you're cousins after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.38,1:35:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔向来有点老派\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael was always a little old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.05,1:35:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他解释说 你多么不可能参与我的合法生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Explain to him how, you can never be part of my, legitimate world.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.71,1:35:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你想要自立门户\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That you want your own family.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.92,1:35:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能接下乔伊·札萨身后的摊子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could straighten out with Joey Zasa left behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.72,1:35:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能够用你的友谊说服他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you could use your friendship to persuade him
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.74,1:35:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远承你的情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would be indebted to you forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.51,1:35:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A Corleone
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.48,1:35:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂得这种朋友的价值\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}knows the value of such a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.01,1:35:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你愿意为我做事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, then, you would work for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.28,1:35:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Si.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.05,1:35:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻你的手，唐·阿尔托贝洛{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bacio la mano, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.22,1:35:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.87,1:35:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他暗示 要你背叛我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if he hints that he wants you to betray me
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.96,1:35:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有被侮辱的样子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}get insulted.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.40,1:35:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是他的陷阱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Because that's his trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.57,1:36:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有告诉我所有实情，文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're not telling me the whole truth, Vincenzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.85,1:36:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是真的，要是迈克尔没了，那女孩就控制一切？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Isn't it true, with Michael gone, the girl controls everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.66,1:36:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别扯上那女孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You leave the girl out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.23,1:36:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  你爱她  她也爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course, you love her. And she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.08,1:36:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜中了吧  文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guessed it Vincenzo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.52,1:36:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是位智者  唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're a wise man, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.82,1:36:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟你学到很多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going to be learning a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.63,1:36:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最富有的人是拥有最多权贵朋友的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The richest man is the one with the most powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.60,1:37:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有责任引介\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my duty to make the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.11,1:37:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.85,1:37:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛告诉我 你有良好的品质：坚强\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello tells me you have good character, strong
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.35,1:37:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个值得尊重的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a man of respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.79,1:37:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是送乔伊·札萨入土的英雄\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is the hero who put Joey Zasa in his grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.62,1:37:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们早知道他的存在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we'd known of his existence
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.35,1:37:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根本就不用支持乔伊了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we would never have backed Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.10,1:37:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人想要再来一个乔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No one wants another Joe
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.06,1:37:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我当你的朋友吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.90,1:37:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便最强大的人也需要朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even the strongest man needs friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.04,1:37:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深感荣幸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.54,1:37:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是金融和政治人物，唐·卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're a man of finance and politics, Don Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.27,1:37:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事我不懂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}these are things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.71,1:37:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂枪吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You understand guns?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.08,1:37:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金融就是一把枪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Finance is a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.55,1:37:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Politics
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.81,1:37:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是知道何时该扣扳机\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}is knowing when to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.31,1:38:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮什么忙？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.55,1:38:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vieni?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.00,1:38:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受保佑的是追求和平的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Blessed is the peacemaker
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.94,1:38:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他可以被称为是神的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for he can be called a child of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.07,1:38:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 会说一点意大利语吗？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}  - 会{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Tu parli Italiano un poco? -Si.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.46,1:38:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·汤马西诺的轮椅{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The wheelchair, for Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.01,1:38:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信了总主教对这笔生意的安排\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trusted this business arrangement with the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.68,1:38:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任他，我当时确信他的诚实经得起质疑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trusted him. I was sure his honesty was beyond a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.88,1:39:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，你也看见了，我现在成了诈骗的受害者\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But, as you see, I'm now the victim of a swindle.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.02,1:39:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在拖延我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's stalling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.06,1:39:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨额的钱财都到了身居高位的大政客手里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vast money have gone to the pezzonovante in high political places
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.17,1:39:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而梵蒂冈银行就是担保人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and the Vatican Bank is the guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.15,1:39:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你所言属实\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If uh, what you say is true
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.67,1:39:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是个大丑闻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}there will be a great scandal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.44,1:39:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这块石头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look at this stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.32,1:39:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它泡在水里已经很久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It has been lying in the water for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.65,1:39:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但水仍然没有能够浸透它\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but the water has not penetrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.25,1:39:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.80,1:39:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Perfectly dry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.49,1:39:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的情况也发生在欧洲人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The same thing has happened to men in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.17,1:39:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数世纪以来，他们一直为基督教所包围\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For centuries they have been surrounded by Christianity
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.03,1:39:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但基督一直没渗入其中\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but Christ has not penetrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.90,1:39:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基督没有与他们同呼吸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Christ doesn't breathe within them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.81,1:39:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.91,1:40:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能的话 给我点甜的东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is it possible, that you could get me something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.51,1:40:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙汁  随便什么  糖果\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Orange juice, anything, candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.42,1:40:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有糖尿病\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Trouble with diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.43,1:40:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血糖水平必须得低\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Blood sugar levels must be low.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.43,1:40:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.72,1:40:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我压力大时有时就会发生这种事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I'm under stress sometimes this happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.59,1:40:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.19,1:40:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I come to you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.51,1:40:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这种微妙的事件\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}on such a delicate matter
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.87,1:40:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指控你们的总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}accusations against your Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.30,1:40:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言是很难的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}was difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.24,1:41:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心煎熬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The mind suffers
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.57,1:41:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体反应在外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and the body, cries out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.30,1:41:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.80,1:41:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想…做告解？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Would you like, to make your confession?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.43,1:41:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Eminence, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.80,1:41:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm uh
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.45,1:41:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's been so long,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.51,1:41:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不  不  不知道从哪里...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wouldn't, wouldn't, wouldn't know where to uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.40,1:41:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经30年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's been thirty years
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.58,1:41:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我会耗用你太多时间的，我觉得\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd, I'd, I'd use up too much of your time, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.75,1:41:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是有时间拯救灵魂的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always have time to save souls.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.65,1:41:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.16,1:41:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经罪无可恕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm beyond redemption.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.53,1:41:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.87,1:42:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会倾听我们这里自己的神父告解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hear the confessions of my own priests here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.90,1:42:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候要告解的愿望无可阻挡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sometimes the desire to confess is overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.32,1:42:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就得把握时机\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and we must seize the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.18,1:42:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我没有悔意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is the point of confessing
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.65,1:42:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告解有什么用？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if I don't repent?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.39,1:42:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你是个实际的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hear you are a practical man
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.86,1:42:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有什么可损失呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What have you got to lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.73,1:42:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.92,1:42:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.49,1:42:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛了我妻子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}betrayed my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.09,1:43:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说下去 我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.33,1:43:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背叛了我自己\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I betrayed myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.04,1:43:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀过人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed men.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.74,1:43:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也曾下令杀过人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I ordered men to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.65,1:43:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着说 我的孩子 接着说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son, go on
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.05,1:43:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉，这没用\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.16,1:43:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧 我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.33,1:43:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.73,1:43:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下令杀死了我的兄弟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I ordered the death of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.60,1:43:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他伤害了我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He injured me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.84,1:43:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我母亲的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.83,1:43:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我母亲的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.57,1:44:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的罪过是可怕的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your sins are terrible
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.96,1:44:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你因此饱受折磨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and it is just that you suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.75,1:44:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人生可获得救赎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your life could be redeemed
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.20,1:44:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你并不相信这一点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I know that you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.58,1:44:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会改变\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You will not change.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.93,1:44:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇保禄六世{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pope Paul VI
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.26,1:44:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马天主教廷至尊教宗{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Supreme Pontiff of the Roman Catholic Church
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.80,1:44:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于昨晚九时四十分辞世{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}died last night at 9:40pm
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.04,1:44:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享年八十一岁{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope was 81 years old
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.15,1:45:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去数月来一直受病痛折磨{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and had been in poor health for the last several months
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.42,1:45:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.66,1:45:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一生，都在尽力走向社会上层\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all my life I, kept trying to go up in society
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.90,1:45:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里一切更高的东西合法、干净\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}where everything higher up was legal, straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.64,1:45:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我爬得越高，它就变得越扭曲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But the higher I go, the crookeder it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.91,1:45:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底会怎么结束？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How in the hell does it end?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.25,1:45:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里互相残杀几个世纪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Killing each other for centuries here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.96,1:45:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For money
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.83,1:45:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为尊严 为家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for pride, for family.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.30,1:45:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了免于沦为富有大亨的奴隶\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To keep from becoming the slaves of the rich pezzonovante.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.41,1:46:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了告解，康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I made confession, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.55,1:46:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坦白了我的罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I confessed my sins.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.28,1:46:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么，迈克尔？这可不像你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why Michael, that's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.12,1:46:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必对一个陌生人坦白罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't have to confess your sins to a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.52,1:46:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.23,1:46:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.60,1:46:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的神父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A true priest.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.87,1:46:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他改变了事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He changed things.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.37,1:46:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.24,1:46:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you know
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.38,1:46:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我想起可怜的弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}sometimes I think of poor Fredo
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.35,1:46:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溺亡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.32,1:46:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是天意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.95,1:46:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个可怕的意外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.52,1:46:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它结束了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.80,1:46:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.80,1:47:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远会帮你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll always help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.27,1:47:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.61,1:47:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛 太荣幸了{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I am honored, Don Altobello
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.45,1:47:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还从巴勒莫来探望我{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that you've come from Palermo to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.09,1:48:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小孩，他长大了{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, the little kid! He's grown.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.76,1:48:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我学个毛驴{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do the donkey for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.85,1:48:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我们当初一起做买卖{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's been some time
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.42,1:48:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很久了{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}since we did business together.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.79,1:48:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,套句美国话{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You are my 'ace in the hole'
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.36,1:48:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我盖着的王牌{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}as we say in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.06,1:48:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个疥癣之疾{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a stone in my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.36,1:48:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我除掉{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You can remove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.11,1:48:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个吗？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only one stone?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.21,1:48:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个就很危险{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.92,1:48:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个有名的人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A famous man.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.05,1:49:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要格外小心{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You will have to take precautions.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.42,1:49:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我做什么你说{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.16,1:49:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我会开价{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then I will tell you my price.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.17,1:49:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多好的面包{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ah, what bread!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.07,1:49:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橄榄油{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ah, olive oil
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.48,1:49:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初榨的{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Virgin...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.00,1:49:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西西里独有{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}only in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.62,1:49:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致敬{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A salute!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.32,1:49:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致死亡{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A morte!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.11,1:49:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.87,1:49:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, Connie! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.25,1:49:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  好想你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.71,1:50:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦，你好，迈克尔  - 你好，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Well, hello Michael. -Hello Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.98,1:50:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 看这个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mom, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.78,1:50:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"乡间骑士"\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.52,1:50:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，道格拉斯不能来太可惜了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know it's too bad that Douglas couldn't be with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.79,1:50:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，我知道，他很想来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, I know. He wanted to come very much,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.83,1:50:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他有一场重要的官司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but he had a very important trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.71,1:50:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道他一定想来  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I know he wanted to come. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.77,1:50:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，你儿子是个艺术家了，嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, your son's an artist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.84,1:50:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  应该谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yes. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.54,1:50:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, what for?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.58,1:50:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢你逼我放他走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For making me, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.18,1:50:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过这么多年…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After all these years
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.52,1:50:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于第一次来到西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here I am in Sicily for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.92,1:50:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拍张你俩在一起的照片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want to get a picture of you together.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.22,1:50:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.22,1:50:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，爸爸，微笑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey dad, smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.36,1:50:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你还带着艾尔·奈利，为什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I see you still have Al Neri. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.47,1:50:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我需要他，他帮我上下车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I need him. He helps me get in and out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.17,1:51:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我提公事包\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Carry my briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.34,1:51:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在撒谎，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're still a liar Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.23,1:51:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你看看西西里，真正的西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me show you Sicily. The real Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.65,1:51:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以稍微多了解一点家族历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe you'll understand the family history a little better.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.70,1:51:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我认为我了解已经够多了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh I think I understand it well enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.35,1:51:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.00,1:52:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.67,1:52:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件东西，是你很久前给我的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have something you made for me a very long time ago
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.71,1:52:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会给你带来好运\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It may bring you luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.58,1:52:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保留着它？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You saved it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.32,1:52:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你还记得吗？  - 我记得\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Remember? -I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.16,1:52:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.43,1:52:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你骄傲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.83,1:52:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.42,1:52:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有外表那么厉害吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Are they as good as they look?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.50,1:52:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更厉害，他们是最好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're better. They're the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.99,1:52:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他们在身边，迈克尔叔叔一定安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As long as they're around, Uncle Michael is safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.52,1:53:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.76,1:53:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你父亲我回来吃晚饭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell your father I'll be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.40,1:53:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.23,1:53:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.37,1:53:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉托尼一定要等我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And tell Tony to be sure to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.13,1:53:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，我会的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay. I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.05,1:53:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bye mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.04,1:53:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好，女士{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Buon giorno, Signora.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.96,1:53:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您吩咐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}At your service
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.68,1:53:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我见到爸爸，会告诉他你走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If I see dad, I'll tell him you left
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.95,1:53:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这家族里剩下唯一有我父亲那种力量的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You are the only one left in this family with my father's strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.83,1:53:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如迈克尔出了什么事，我要你还击\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If anything happens to Michael, I want you to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.83,1:53:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让人准备好一切\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll have everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.31,1:53:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发誓？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You swear?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.45,1:53:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.45,1:54:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.80,1:54:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲出生的房子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The house where my father was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.55,1:54:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是来这里…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is where they came
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.69,1:54:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要带走还是孩子的他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to take him when he was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.10,1:54:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.23,1:54:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.70,1:54:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.72,1:55:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗，玛丽恋爱了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, Mary's in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.22,1:55:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.09,1:55:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一个英俊的意大利男人，黑眼睛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}With a handsome young Italian man. Dark eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.40,1:55:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会允许的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't allow it
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.90,1:55:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是错误的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.67,1:55:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错误而且危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's wrong and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.11,1:55:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲，我的父亲{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh father, my father!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.28,1:55:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一点时间向主祈祷{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give me some time to pray to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.18,1:55:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡里尼男爵夫人对丈夫不贞{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Baroness of Carini had betrayed her husband
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.62,1:55:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同她的堂兄相恋{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and fallen in love with her cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.92,1:55:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可饶恕{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There will be no forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.46,1:55:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的父亲刺向她{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Her father stabbed her
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.86,1:55:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一剑穿心{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}through the heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.07,1:56:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉，是吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Honor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.29,1:56:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗，我想起那次你来我父母家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, I remember the time that you came to my parent's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.18,1:56:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我带进房间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you took me into that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.95,1:56:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的家族生意…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you told me about the family business
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.81,1:56:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你是如何不会跟它有任何牵连\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and how you were never going to have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.55,1:56:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那口气就像托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You sounded like Tony
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.12,1:56:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时是很像托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was a lot like Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.65,1:56:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几乎看不见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I can barely see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.86,1:56:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 凯伊  - 什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Kay. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.90,1:56:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来开车吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you mind driving?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.76,1:56:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行，怎么了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.22,1:56:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛，有时侯还好，不过…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My eyes. Sometimes they're all right. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.09,1:56:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有，我得去见唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, I have to see Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.73,1:56:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，夫人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Benday, signora.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.60,1:57:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没有随身保镖啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's no bodyguards today.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.57,1:57:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是偷跑出来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really snuck away.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.28,1:57:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父，你们去哪儿？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Father, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.65,1:57:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要搭便车吗？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&} Would you like a ride?"
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.33,1:57:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认得你{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.63,1:57:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是蒙特莱普家的莫斯卡{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're Mosca of Montelepre.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.33,1:57:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前当过杀手{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were an assassin then
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.07,1:57:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也是杀手{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and you're an assassin now
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.23,1:57:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，我知道迈克尔·柯利昂尼在你家{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know Michael Corleone is at your house.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.27,1:57:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟着你通过大门{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will pass through the gates with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.42,1:58:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.13,1:58:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊，这是卡洛，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay, this is Calo, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.14,1:58:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前的一个保镖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One of my bodyguards in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.24,1:58:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们可以在这里等他  - 要喝一杯吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We can wait here. -You want drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.77,1:58:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我们进去？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.24,1:58:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这房间度过了很多时间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent a lot of time in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.31,1:58:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.39,1:58:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你结婚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then you got married.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.29,1:58:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然想着你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I still thought of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.69,1:58:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个房间里有什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's in that room?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.37,1:58:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这对你很危险，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know this is dangerous for you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.90,1:58:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.97,1:58:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱这地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.51,1:58:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.48,1:58:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个历史上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, all through history
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.58,1:58:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有可怕的事情发生在这些人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}terrible things have happened to these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.85,1:59:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕而不公的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Terrible injustice.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.15,1:59:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们依旧期待好的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But they still expect good
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.26,1:59:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是坏事情发生在自己身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}rather than bad will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.56,1:59:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我和你？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sort of like me and you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.63,1:59:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How so?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.73,1:59:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然在这里，对吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well I'm still here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.20,1:59:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有糟糕的过去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We do have a bad history
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.51,1:59:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.74,1:59:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，你还在，但心存畏惧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yes you are. But with dread.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.01,1:59:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下命令吧，来吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gimme the order! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.35,1:59:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么意义呢？这样能让我不畏惧你？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's that supposed to do, is that supposed to make me not dread you?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.82,1:59:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在西西里，歌剧嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We’re in Sicily, the opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.56,1:59:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.46,1:59:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.17,1:59:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.74,1:59:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们努力不要互相伤害\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's try not to hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.71,2:00:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你原谅我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.62,2:00:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For what?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.89,2:00:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.43,2:00:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，像上帝那样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, like God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.23,2:00:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我需要更为亲近些\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, I, I need something a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.80,2:00:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能理解那些日子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You couldn’t understand, back in those days.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.47,2:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱我的父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love my father
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.61,2:00:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾发誓不会成为他那样的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swore I would never be, a man like him
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.58,2:00:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我爱他  而他又身处险境\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I loved him. And he was in danger
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.38,2:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.98,2:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后来，你有危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then later, you were in danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.55,2:00:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的孩子们，有危险，我能怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our children, were in danger. what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.92,2:00:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全是我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were all that I...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.82,2:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上最爱、最珍惜的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...loved, valued, most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.50,2:00:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我正要失去你，最终失去了你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And, I'm losing you, I lost you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.97,2:00:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're gone
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.97,2:01:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切成了徒劳\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and it was all for nothing
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.45,2:01:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.48,2:01:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须理解，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you have to understand, I...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.22,2:01:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时计划了整个不一样的命运\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I had a whole different destiny planned.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.15,2:01:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我不说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, I'll stop
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.60,2:01:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不知道你要我怎么做，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really don’t know what you want from me, Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.60,2:01:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.97,2:01:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I mean
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.77,2:01:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是你想像的那种人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not the man that you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.94,2:01:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.31,2:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.25,2:01:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再畏惧我了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't dread me, anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.12,2:01:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.42,2:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西西里这里的每一个晚上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}every night here in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.10,2:01:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做梦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I dream
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.17,2:02:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦见我的妻子和我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}about my wife and my children.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.70,2:02:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如何失去他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And how I lost them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.81,2:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…如果这能有所安慰的话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guess, if it's any consolation
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.38,2:02:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你知道…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to know that
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.02,2:02:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.42,2:02:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直爱你，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always loved you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.32,2:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你知道吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you know...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.72,2:02:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直，一直爱下去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always, I always will.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.49,2:03:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.43,2:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们发现唐·汤马西诺中枪了{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They found Don Tommasino shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.80,2:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.60,2:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主人死了，血债要血偿{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My master is dead. Blood calls for blood.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.64,2:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要报仇{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I must have revenge
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.95,2:03:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天，你可能的为我办一件难事{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Some day, you may have to do a difficult service for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.00,2:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管吩咐{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Command me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.52,2:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为他报仇的{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will avenge him
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.05,2:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Siri
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.32,2:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙巴度\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lamberto
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.44,2:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗塞德\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lorscheider
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.81,2:03:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总计\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Totals
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.34,2:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗塞德  1票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lorscheider, 1 vote.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.65,2:03:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西里  11票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Siri, 11 votes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.25,2:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙巴度  99票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lamberto, 99 votes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.13,2:04:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否接受推举{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you accept your election
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.60,2:04:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担任教皇至尊？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}as supreme pontiff?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.07,2:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝明鉴  赐福吾同僚之决策{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My God, shed light on the decision they have taken on my behalf
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.44,2:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I accept.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.44,2:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望以何名义为称号？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}By what name do you wish to be called?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.08,2:04:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若望·保禄一世{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}John Paul the First.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.02,2:05:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将即刻执事{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will do things 'right away'
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.45,2:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不愿有所拖延{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}rather than in 'a little while.'
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.68,2:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}弗雷德里克·凯恩济格，过去十年里的“上帝的银行家”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Frederik Keinszig, known for a decade as "God's banker,"
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.26,2:05:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}被报告失踪，最后被见于3天前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has been reported missing. He was last seen three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.12,2:05:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}离开梵蒂冈所有的“屹莫比国际”公司在罗马的办公室\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}leaving the Rome offices of the Vatican owned corporation International Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.56,2:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}随之失踪的还有大笔款项 及多份文件\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Also missing was a large sum of money, and several documents.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.53,2:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接啊，凯恩济格，你这蠢货\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Keinszig, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.04,2:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}凯恩济格先生的失踪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Keinszig's absence
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.81,2:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}引起了对梵蒂冈银行交易的更多疑窦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}casts further suspicion on the dealings of the Vatican bank.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.21,2:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}多年以来该银行及其下属子公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For several years the bank and its subsidiary companies
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.08,2:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一直被指为不名誉商业活动的对象\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}have been the object of allegations of disreputable business practices.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.23,2:05:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}这些活动包括…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These practices include...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.79,2:05:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢凯西  请你尽量要了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lucchesi, will you please try and understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.16,2:05:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打电话找过他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have phoned him.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.03,2:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在等他的电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have waited here by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.43,2:05:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要记住，卢凯西先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You would do well to remember, Mr. Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.43,2:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一位教皇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that this Pope
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.96,2:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与上一位有着非常不一样的想法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has very, different ideas from the last one.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.37,2:06:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Goodbye my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.94,2:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本可以活得更久一点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could have lived a little longer
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.57,2:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本可以更接近我的梦想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could be closer to my dream.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.32,2:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你深受爱戴，唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were so loved, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.89,2:06:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我这么令人害怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why was I so feared
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.39,2:06:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你如此受爱戴？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and you so loved?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.89,2:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么原因？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.53,2:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不乏体面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was no less honorable.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.91,2:07:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想做好事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted to do good.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.05,2:07:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么背弃了我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What betrayed me?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.12,2:07:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头脑？我的心？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My mind? My heart?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.96,2:07:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要这样谴责自己？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why do I condemn myself so?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.95,2:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.26,2:07:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我子女的性命发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}on the lives of my children
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.05,2:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一个机会挽回自己\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give me a chance to redeem myself
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.72,2:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将不再犯下罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I will sin, no more.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.18,2:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸色不好  有坏消息\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You look pale. Bad news.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.32,2:08:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接告诉我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell me right away
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.42,2:08:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不单是一次糟糕的银行交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not just a bad banking deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.12,2:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人就是屠夫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These guys are butchers.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.26,2:08:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪些人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What guys?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.23,2:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lucchesi.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.76,2:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他控制了他们全体\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He controls all of them
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.30,2:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Altobello,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.82,2:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.48,2:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更高的人，也许有P2{\fs12}[不懂啥意思]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}other people higher up, P2, maybe
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.36,2:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的，未知的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Secret, unknown.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.57,2:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在操作事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're running things.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.04,2:08:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挡了他们的路\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm in their way.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.24,2:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.95,2:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他雇了个职业杀手要杀你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's hired a professional assassin to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.51,2:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西西里人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's Sicilian.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.08,2:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道名字\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know his name,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.18,2:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说他从未失过手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but they say he never fails.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.60,2:08:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁也不安全了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then no one is safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.58,2:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连新教皇也很危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even the new pope is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.18,2:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有时间，我们能预防\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We still have time. We can prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.51,2:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I tried
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.11,2:09:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincen
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.01,2:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I tried
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.08,2:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要避免一切走到这一步\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to keep everything from coming to this.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.02,2:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是不可能\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But it's not possible,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.96,2:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界不可能\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}not in this world.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.22,2:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下命令吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give me the order.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.76,2:09:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就没有回头路了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You won't be able to go back.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.02,2:09:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会像我一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'll be like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.60,2:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.96,2:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一辈子都想退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All my life I wanted out.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.80,2:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想要家族退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted the family out.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.93,2:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I don't want out.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.31,2:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要权力来维系家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want the power to preserve the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.78,2:10:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请求你下命令\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm asking for the order.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.90,2:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's done.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.15,2:10:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不能再做下去了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Because I can't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.10,2:10:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.55,2:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特知道该做什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent knows what to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.40,2:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，出去吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.07,2:10:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下，别再费心了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take a rest and don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.70,2:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的就是替大家费心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All I do is think about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.25,2:10:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm your son.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.84,2:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情都交给我吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Command me in all things.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.22,2:10:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃我女儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give up my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.16,2:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你要付的代价\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's the price you pay
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.43,2:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你选择的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for the life you choose.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.92,2:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侄子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nephew
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.69,2:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此刻起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}from this moment on
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.43,2:11:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可自称文森特·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}call yourself Vincent Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.80,2:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.32,2:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.16,2:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}，康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazie Connie.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.76,2:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.87,2:12:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·文森佐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Vincenzo Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:59.98,2:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.41,2:13:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（“乡间骑士”歌剧）
Dialogue: 0,2:13:44.76,2:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Et Tu, Vincenzo
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.30,2:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你对迈克尔的感情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know how you feel about Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.27,2:13:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你救不了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but you, you can't save him.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.74,2:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他迷失了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.71,2:13:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为自己考虑一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Think of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.68,2:14:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的答案是什么，文森特？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's your answer, Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.15,2:14:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好欣赏歌剧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Enjoy the opera.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.98,2:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都安排好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's all taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.39,2:14:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查酒吧，我去检查屋顶\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Check the bar. I'll check the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.97,2:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿安东尼在马克西莫剧院演唱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here's hoping Tony sings better at Theatre Maximo
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.10,2:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜过他在洗澡时的歌声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}than he does in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.84,2:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的康斯坦琪娅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My darling, Constanzia.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.50,2:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.28,2:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个大场面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a great occasion.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.04,2:14:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  坐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.82,2:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.09,2:14:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你80岁了，看起来没超过60\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're eighty years old。 You don't look more than sixty.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.66,2:14:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是唯一记得的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're the only one who remembered.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.92,2:14:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我们刚收到消息\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, we just got the word.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.70,2:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇批准了“屹莫比”的交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope's ratified the Immobiliare deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.53,2:14:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've won.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.30,2:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.73,2:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世事多么难料\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How strange, the way things work.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.24,2:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇在做的正是你说他会做的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope's doing exactly what you said he'd do
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.07,2:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在清理门户\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he's cleaning house.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.00,2:15:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该小心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.04,2:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个诚实的人会有危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's dangerous to be an honest man.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.35,2:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加派人手到后台保护托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanna put a little more muscle backstage with Tony
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.50,2:15:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前过生日总请我吃东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}On your birthday, you used to shower me with treats.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.90,2:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油卷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tootsie Rolls!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.64,2:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作这些奶油卷的修女发誓缄口\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The nuns who made these cannolis took a vow of silence.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.21,2:15:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最优质的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're the very finest.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.88,2:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, coz.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.56,2:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的皮衣呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where's your leather?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.46,2:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.93,2:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么瘦，你来吃\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're so thin. You eat it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:23.89,2:16:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，谢谢，谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}E buono. Grazie, grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.99,2:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's over, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.43,2:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情不得不做，你不能参与\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There are things I have to do that you can't be a part of.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.50,2:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看你父亲，这不是你父亲的决定，是我的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't look at your father, it's not your father's decision, it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:40.17,2:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要恨你父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't hate your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.61,2:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事情我要参与，你不能在身边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There are things I'm going to be part of, you can't be around.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.21,2:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚之后，你再也不会见到我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After tonight, you won't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.92,2:16:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.42,2:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得理解，玛丽，你得理解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You gotta understand, Mary. You gotta understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:02.06,2:17:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.77,2:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱别人吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Love somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.37,2:17:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬托尼  敬托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To Tony! To Tony!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.90,2:21:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会做什么了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They won't try anything
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.15,2:21:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，一切正常，这边都安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, everything’s fine. It's all clear out here.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.90,2:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派艾尔·奈利去了梵蒂冈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've already sent Al Neri to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.98,2:21:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 卢凯西先生的房子？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}  - 是{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Mr. Lucchesi's house? -Si.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.35,2:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带来迈克尔·柯利昂尼的口信{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I bring a message from Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.93,2:21:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进来{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.42,2:23:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.34,2:26:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你搞掂他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good, you got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:16.57,2:27:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上柯利昂尼家族要算帐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tonight the Corleone family settles its accounts.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:20.28,2:27:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯恩济格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Keinszig
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.58,2:27:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个他妈的瑞士小银行家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that little Swiss banker fuck
Dialogue: 0,2:27:26.32,2:27:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从一开始就在玩弄每一个人，操他妈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he's been swindling everyone from the beginning. Fuck 'im.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.57,2:27:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·卢凯西，我的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Lucchesi. My friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.46,2:27:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛会去拜访他，在他家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Calo will pay him a visit at his home.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:39.76,2:27:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈利\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Neri
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.63,2:27:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭火车去罗马\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}take a train to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.60,2:27:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为总主教点一根蜡烛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Light a candle for the Archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:23.00,2:28:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶，陛下，有助于你的睡眠{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tea, your holiness? It will help you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.88,2:28:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是文森特·柯利昂尼给你的{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is from Vincent Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:50.08,2:29:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，事情严重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, it's serious.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.36,2:29:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在梵蒂冈内部的人说 有人要暗算教宗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our man inside the Vatican says there's a plot against the Pope.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:55.10,2:29:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说晚上他会发心脏病？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You mean he's going to have a heart attack in the night.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.51,2:30:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位教皇有强大的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This Pope has powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:07.05,2:30:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能没法及时救他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We may not be in time to save him.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:12.44,2:30:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们回去看歌剧吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now let's go back to the opera.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.62,2:30:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}
Dialogue: 0,2:30:42.96,2:30:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇陛下{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.72,2:30:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至圣？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Eminenza?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:56.12,2:30:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至圣？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Eminenza?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:58.76,2:31:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至圣？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Eminenza?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:04.40,2:31:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣父死了{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Holy Father is dead!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:39.10,2:32:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:41.27,2:32:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧，教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sleep, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:58.65,2:32:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以进吗？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Posso entrare io?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:53.57,2:33:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧...告诉我{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Speak...tell me.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:55.71,2:34:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已失去了…{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have lost
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.24,2:34:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的信心{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the faith of the people.
